{"tid":1713442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［建議］","createTime":"2019-11-12T17:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T18:41:54.000Z","uid":183051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3416b09e84a6ed2b0e6ed3def8e8dc8e76aa16ad","tid":1713442,"uid":183051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"1.  班object呢排肆意出嚟，我地係咪應該集中主力去佢地應該保護既地方，咁佢先會由主導轉為被動。<br />\n<br />\n2. 有無可能自制細型（枝頭點燃）弓箭取代人手火魔法<br />\n<br />\n3. 覺唔覺呢刻香港各區 有時call 人 出嚟會比較困難？ 當無咗交通工具，靠既係街坊，但而家街坊間個關係此終唔夠，可能有事上嚟，佢直行直過或者只係以旁觀者身份睇住件事發生，幫手個動機少咗。<br />\n<br />\n所以，就算而家和理非既，應該要搵定多幾個人合作，到有事需要你既時候行動上都方便啲。另外，街坊鄰里彼此應該要接觸多啲，搵人落樓下、傳消息、互相幫助呢點對日後行動都有好大幫助<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e450bbb228b0a666d5b01597d73df0330cc4a7c2","tid":1713442,"uid":183051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:33:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7892de5b8ee1f3c82d76d320bb376ca8d4a27aeb","tid":1713442,"uid":183051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"40a99f3f97e393b13a9f667b7eacbffab9f1cbf7","tid":1713442,"uid":183051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"31285f0fb7646a318fc1141d54737fec90ed6b5b","tid":1713442,"uid":183051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125a91b76be16cda22898630f271e59a8dc0a229","tid":1713442,"uid":183051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"